ate&amp;sv_campaign_id=1412197&amp;awc=28987_1698431525_dddc29aada0f4dbee711469001680b18" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买。</p><p>与此同时，达尔特雷目前也正在进行他自己的激情项目—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/new-keith-moon-biopic-to-reportedly-begin-shooting-this-summer-3151017">一部关于乐队已故鼓手基思·穆恩的传记片</a>。</p><p>皮特·汤<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pete-townshend-says-the-who-will-have-a-talk-about-what-happens-next-3556537">森德 (Pete Townshend) 表示 The Who 将讨论“接下来会发生什么”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
